name: Report to governor
text:
§157-18  Report to governor.  At the end of each license year, the board of agriculture shall submit to the governor a report relating to the activities of the milk control program. [L 1967, c 260, §11; HRS §157-18; am L 1986, c 61, §2]
 
Cross References
 
  Annual reports, see §93-12.
